  "text": "We consider the following research questions: RQ1 How effective is our approach as compared to standard diff and DiffCat [CITATION_1] in identifying root causes? RQ2 How effective is our essential change extraction component? RQ3 How effective is our filtering component? RQ4 How effective is our propagation component? RQ5 How effective is our approach when less training data is used? RQ6 How efficient is our solution? How much time does our approach need to extract root causes from bug-fixing file changes?",
